content.text: Trial 4/5, Stage 'ytraverse1': Please describe the image and compute the stiffness matrix.

The image shows a section of the groove highlighted by a red circle, which primarily runs along the Y-axis.

**Stiffness Matrix Computation:**

2. Assign 250 N/m to Y, and 100 N/m to X and Z.
